sequenceDiagram
  participant M as Model
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant P as Permission
  participant FS as File System
  participant S as State

  M->>T: Read(package.json)
  T->>P: check read path
  P-->>T: allow
  T->>FS: read file with limit
  FS-->>T: content + mtime
  T->>S: update readFileState
  T-->>M: observation with lines

  M->>T: Edit(src/sum.ts, old, new)
  T->>S: verify prior read baseline
  T->>P: check write permission
  P-->>T: ask or allow
  T->>FS: apply unique replacement
  FS-->>T: new content + diff
  T->>S: update readFileState and audit
  T-->>M: observation with diff summary
